title: New: JUDE. – Can’t Breathe
content:
FL duo JUDE.

are already one of the most blogged about new outfits of 2014, and their latest single, Can’t Breathe started doing the rounds last week. Again characterised by the Lorde meets Ellie Goulding style vocals of Sydney Morris, and the M83-esque production from Kevin James Neal. Their most ambitious and ‘pop’ sounding track to date, it’s an exciting taster from an EP titled The Bedroom, expected out later this year.
